<h4>From May 2018 – October 2018:</h4>

<ol class="achievement-list">
<li>We have completed the installation of over 63 782  new light fittings across HCPS. Remember this is not a re-lamp project; it is a full replacement of aged and inefficient fixtures with state of the art LED fixtures. Take a moment: Minimise USA making News on Good Morning Tampa Bay</li>  
<li>Designed, built and installed a chiller system at Edison Elementary School. This was the first of its kind, design/build project at HCPS where Minimise and its local partners reinvented the cooling infrastructure at this city of Tampa school.</li>
<li>Also at Edison Elementary, we started with the design and implementation of the first covered Solar panel parking lot. Once completed, this along with other global initiatives will offset over 42% of its energy consumption.</li>
