<li>We started the first of its kind Zero Waste Cooling Tower project at Chamberlain High School. The success of this pilot is the catalyst in the use or reduction of chemicals, along with maintenance and energy savings technology.</li>
<li>Eniscope, Minimise’ real time energy consumption monitoring system, was installed at over 80 schools.  (We will have an Eniscope at the November 2018, FSFOA conference for you to inspect, exam and ask questions about.)</li>
